<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>٥ كلمات<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>١ -<span style="color:#006d98"> لزم:</span><a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>أ-<span style="color:#006d98"> لزم الشئ يلزم:</span> وجب وأصبح لزاما أي ضروريا<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>ب-<span style="color:#006d98"> لزمه يلزمه:</span> صحبه لا يفارقه.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>٢ -<span style="color:#006d98"> ألزم:</span><a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>أ-<span style="color:#006d98"> ألزمته الشئ:</span> جعلته واجبا عليه.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>